# Battle Ships
```
bind @browser
	[#h1 text:"BattleShip"]
```
```
search 
  i = range[from: 1 to: 10]
  j = range[from: 1 to: 10]

commit
	[#sp x:i y:j col:"white" text:""]
```

```eve
search
	min = 1
  max = 10
	x = range[from:min to: max]
  y = round[value: random[seed: x] * (max - min) + min]
 
commit
  [#ship x: x y: y name:"ship {{x}}"]
```

```

search 
	sp = [#sp x y text]
  order = sort[value: (x y)]
  
bind @browser
[#div style: [display: "flex", flex-direction:"row", flex-wrap: "wrap", border-style: "solid", border-width: "1"] children:
  [#div sort: order sp text: "{{sp.text}}" style: [flex: "auto" width:"10%", height:"50", border-style: "solid" border-color:"gray", text-align:"center" background-color:"{{sp.col}}"]]]
```


```
search @event @session @browser
	[#click element: [#div sp]]
  (col, txt) = if [#ship x:sp.x y:sp.y name] then ("#FD5549", "{{name}}")
  			else ("#708AD7", "MISS")
commit
	sp <- [col: col text:txt] 
  
```
